# Medical Presentation Framework — .gitignore

# Development backups and superseded drafts. See CLAUDE.md (top section)
# for what this folder is and why it's excluded.
not-used/

# Backup files anywhere in the tree (safe-file-operations.md convention:
# {file}.backup-YYYYMMDD-HHMM.{ext})
*.backup-*

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# Python build artefacts (in case scripts get added later)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/

# Live working presentation projects — keep the framework repo clean of
# patient-adjacent or in-progress decks. Remove this section if you want
# example projects published alongside the framework.
# (Uncomment the next lines to apply.)
# Departments/
# Rotations/
# Cases/

AGENTS.md
